content:
Mask Customer Phone Numbers

Protect sensitive data by redacting inbound and outbound phone numbers from Omni-Channel views, call recordings, and transcripts.

REQUIRED USER PERMISSIONS:
Customize Application AND Manage Call Centers
Contact Center Admin
Customize Application AND Manage Call Centers
Contact Center Admin (Partner Telephony)

This feature is available with these telephony models: SERVICE CLOUD VOICE WITH AMAZON CONNECT, SERVICE CLOUD VOICE WITH PARTNER TELEPHONY FROM AMAZON CONNECT, SERVICE CLOUD VOICE WITH PARTNER TELEPHONY

After you turn on phone number masking, all phone numbers appear in Omni-Channel views, call recordings, and transcripts as “Masked Number.”

From Setup, in the Quick Find box, enter Amazon Setup or Partner Telephony Setup.
Turn on Mask Phone Numbers.
title: Masking Customer Phone Numbers in Service Cloud
